high_descs: Turn around and walk to the green trash can then turn left to face the tub.
Take the black rag furthest away from out of the tub.
Raise it up and turn around to make a left to face the sink.
Place the rag in the sink and turn on the water. Turn the water off and take the rag back out.
Turn around and take a step. Turn to the right and go back to the tub.
Put the clean rag next to the dirty rag laying in the tub.
anns.task_desc: To clean a rag to put back into the tub.

high_descs: Turn right then left to face tub.
Pick up the cloth from the tub, to the right of the other cloth.
Turn around, proceed to sink, turn left to face sink.
Put cloth in sink, fill and empty sink, pick up cloth.
Place cloth in tub, directly left to the cloth already in the tub.
anns.task_desc: Clean cloth and return to tub.

high_descs: Turn to the right and face the tub.
Pick the black towel up from the right side of the tub.
Turn around and face the sink on the left.
Put the towel in the sink and turn the water on and then turn the water off and pick the towel up.
Turn around and face the tub.
Put the towel in the tub.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean towel in the tub.
